{"tid":897854,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖 ]英攝影師肯尼亞草原遇長頸鹿生產　拍下珍貴生BB過程","createTime":"2018-11-11T09:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T15:44:37.000Z","uid":172024,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"01bd36d678e00c5d6b29faa7d70fe431aefd1652","tid":897854,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"鹿媽生BB：英國攝影師戈德斯坦（Paul Goldstein）與妻兒到肯尼亞旅遊期間，在Olare Motorogi自然保護區目睹一隻母長頸鹿正準備生產，一雙腳出現在長頸鹿的臀部。小長頸鹿前腳先露出，隨後慢慢在母鹿的努力下令頭部和眼睛見於天日。整個分娩過程持續兩小時。長頸鹿的孕期為14到15個月。母長頸鹿生產時是站立着的，因此小長頸鹿脫離子宮時距地面約1.8公尺高、相當危險。 整個分娩過程持續兩小時。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJ3SvFd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJ3SvFd.jpg&h=432b53c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsWAtrU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsWAtrU.jpg&h=15e0bf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jh9eJ0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJh9eJ0f.jpg&h=8bee58e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6EfBcTB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6EfBcTB.jpg&h=91959a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DOBpmMX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDOBpmMX.jpg&h=382b70d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好得意~原來佢地係咁樣生仔....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347408896d2e1dd8dc1b4273a98e227bce3a9a28","tid":897854,"uid":187148,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"好大隻。。"},{"pid":"45fa77ef58cda6b0a9ecee0e37af8dcec1aaa4d6","tid":897854,"uid":201604,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTi